1
00:00:28,580 --> 00:00:33,290
♪Life is a dream♪

2
00:00:33,290 --> 00:00:38,520
♪A dream like chasing the wind♪

3
00:00:39,440 --> 00:00:44,300
♪Yet he is lost within it,
refusing to wake♪

4
00:00:44,470 --> 00:00:48,720
(Wenbo, Puppeteer)
♪The so-called Golden Millet Dream♪

5
00:00:48,760 --> 00:00:52,190
♪Severed between clouds and water♪

6
00:00:52,670 --> 00:00:54,510
(Xuansi Drama Troupe)
♪Looking back once more♪

7
00:00:54,510 --> 00:00:55,790
- Only...
- Bravo!

8
00:01:04,511 --> 00:01:07,000
Since ancient times, it's been said
that when Nuo opera begins,

9
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:08,280
a hundred disasters vanish.

10
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,720
Even though the gods

11
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:12,330
might look like demons,

12
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:14,040
they are actually the ones

13
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,600
who drive away plagues and disasters.

14
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,800
The show is starting!

15
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:18,680
Look!

16
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,044
(Xuansi Drama Troupe)
The Nuo opera is starting!

17
00:01:20,066 --> 00:01:21,180
- Let's go!
- Go, go, go!

18
00:01:21,288 --> 00:01:22,660
Today is the God-Welcoming Dance.

19
00:01:22,670 --> 00:01:24,390
- We get to see Master Zhuang Luobai!
- Yeah!

20
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,960
We get to see Zhuang Luobai today!

21
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,400
Right! Let's go see Zhuang Luobai!

22
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,560
Come on, hurry!

23
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:15,360
If the God-Welcoming Dance
is this grand today,

24
00:02:15,370 --> 00:02:17,200
imagine what
the Winter Festival in seven days

25
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:17,880
will be like.

26
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:18,760
I know, right?

27
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,860
I'm looking forward to the full show

28
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:21,933
at the Winter Festival.

29
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,880
That lady has such a beautiful figure.

30
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,920
Nuo opera has its taboos.

31
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,960
Ladies

32
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,560
are forbidden to touch the masks,

33
00:02:51,760 --> 00:02:53,200
let alone dance.

34
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:55,880
Is he a man?

35
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,600
A man?

36
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,560
How can a man perform Nuo opera

37
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,800
with such grace and beauty?

38
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,320
That's Zhuang Luobai.

39
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,280
He's the only one

40
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,760
playing female roles in the troupe.

41
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,200
He's a true master.

42
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,080
Something seems a bit off.

43
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,880
Looking at his movements today,

44
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,720
he seems to have lost his usual flair.

45
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,200
He fell!

46
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,240
Look! Look!

47
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,360
He's not Zhuang Luobai!

48
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,750
That's not Zhuang Luobai.

49
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:23,970
He's not Zhuang Luobai.

50
00:03:24,020 --> 00:03:24,800
Who is this?

51
00:03:24,810 --> 00:03:26,050
- We want to see Zhuang Luobai!
- That's not Master Zhuang!

52
00:03:26,050 --> 00:03:27,080
- Yeah!
- Is he performing or not?

53
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,440
(Ming Yu)
Isn't that Zhuang Luobai's apprentice,

54
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:29,440
(Nuo Opera Apprentice)
Ming Yu?

55
00:03:29,440 --> 00:03:31,080
Get off! Bring Master Zhuang out!

56
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,210
This dance is nothing
without Master Zhuang.

57
00:03:32,222 --> 00:03:32,977
Ming Yu...

58
00:03:43,260 --> 00:03:46,500
(Zhuang Luobai, Nuo Opera Master)

59
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,200
Master...

60
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,160
What are you doing?

61
00:03:59,290 --> 00:04:00,580
For today's God-Welcoming Dance,

62
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:02,580
you will lead.

63
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,160
Lead the God-Welcoming Dance,

64
00:04:06,888 --> 00:04:08,130
and then the Winter Festival.

65
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:10,810
Dance well today,

66
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:13,222
and you will always be the lead dancer

67
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,320
for the Winter Festival.

68
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:18,570
Master.

69
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,360
Can I really do this?

70
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,880
Don't betray the Troupe Master's trust.

71
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,360
Yes.

72
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:32,560
Master,

73
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:34,960
I will do my best.

74
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,480
It's freezing out here.

75
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,780
How much longer do we have to wait?

76
00:04:38,790 --> 00:04:40,511
- It's so cold!
- Are they still dancing?

77
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,800
We want to see the dance!

78
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:44,150
Exactly!

79
00:04:44,210 --> 00:04:46,320
- We want to see Zhuang Luobai!
- Are they dancing or not?

80
00:04:46,333 --> 00:04:47,230
Where is Zhuang Luobai?

81
00:04:47,230 --> 00:04:49,580
Someone's dead! Someone's dead!

82
00:04:49,970 --> 00:04:52,080
There's a dead body backstage!

83
00:04:56,220 --> 00:05:02,740
=The Tang Mist S1=

84
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:23,380
=Episode 7=

85
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,520
Sir, follow me.

86
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,440
Right over there.

87
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:51,680
It's her.

88
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,680
Why is it her?

89
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:53,560
Divine punishment.

90
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,711
It's divine punishment!

91
00:06:54,755 --> 00:06:55,690
She broke the rules!

92
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:56,920
The gods have punished her!

93
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,640
Do you know the deceased?

94
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,920
She's Master's lover.

95
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,711
Don't talk nonsense.

96
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,560
Who might you be?

97
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,640
Imperial Commissioner of Jiangnan,

98
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,600
Di Renjie.

99
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,160
Oh.

100
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:20,280
I am the Troupe Master.

101
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,480
Greetings, Commissioner Di.

102
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,640
Just now,

103
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,320
why did you call this divine punishment?

104
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,400
What else do you know?

105
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,480
Ming Yu,

106
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,460
you tell him.

107
00:07:33,160 --> 00:07:34,240
Her name is Gu Pan'er.

108
00:07:34,333 --> 00:07:35,480
(Gu Pan'er)
She was Master's

109
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,170
close friend.

110
00:07:37,933 --> 00:07:39,130
How do I look, Master Zhuang?

111
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,140
Don't I look

112
00:07:40,170 --> 00:07:41,080
better than you?

113
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,720
You do.

114
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,400
Master...

115
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:56,200
Master!

116
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:58,840
What has gotten into you?

117
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,760
Has this woman bewitched you?

118
00:08:01,822 --> 00:08:03,280
What nonsense are you spouting?

119
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:04,920
Master,

120
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,355
you've broken the rules
of the Nuo opera.

121
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:13,400
Women cannot perform Nuo opera.

122
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,560
Much less touch the masks.

123
00:08:17,250 --> 00:08:18,080
Since when

124
00:08:18,500 --> 00:08:19,680
is it your place to meddle?

125
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:22,200
Give the mask back to me.

126
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,920
Give it back!

127
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:48,200
You will be punished by the gods.

128
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,080
It was this woman.

129
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:58,280
I saw her wearing the costume
with my own eyes.

130
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,160
She even wore the mask.

131
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:02,000
This must be divine punishment.

132
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,280
Exactly.

133
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,440
It's divine punishment.

134
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,760
She broke the rules.

135
00:09:05,844 --> 00:09:07,000
The gods have passed judgment.

136
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,040
She deserves her death.

137
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:24,910
Her tongue has blackened.

138
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:27,280
Light red lividity has
appeared on the body.

139
00:09:27,333 --> 00:09:28,880
Complete rigor mortis has set in.

140
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,680
The eyes have clouded over.

141
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:32,160
Given the snowy weather

142
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,880
and the cold temperature,

143
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,760
she has been dead for fourteen hours.

144
00:09:36,370 --> 00:09:37,350
It should be

145
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,920
late You hour last night.

146
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:43,320
A person died backstage,

147
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:45,560
and none of you noticed a thing?

148
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,280
Commissioner Di,

149
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:48,680
our theater is divided

150
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,480
into the front, middle,
and back courtyards.

151
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:51,720
We live in the front,

152
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,650
practice in the middle,

153
00:09:52,810 --> 00:09:54,080
and store our props in the back.

154
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:56,480
It snowed heavily last night,
so we didn't perform.

155
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,600
We all stayed in the front.

156
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:59,250
We didn't notice.

157
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:00,160
Yes.

158
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,800
None of us was here last night.

159
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,000
Commissioner Di,

160
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:07,360
it was not poison.

161
00:10:11,933 --> 00:10:14,000
There are strangulation marks
on the victim's neck.

162
00:10:14,010 --> 00:10:15,560
Narrow on the left,
and wide on the right.

163
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:17,560
It indicates the use of the right hand.

164
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,720
On the left side of the neck,

165
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,520
there is a circular puncture wound.

166
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:23,920
The murder weapon appears
to be a woman's hairpin.

167
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,320
This is the fatal wound.

168
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,800
Based on the footprint,

169
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:34,800
the foot length is 27.33 cm.

170
00:11:36,490 --> 00:11:37,400
What?

171
00:11:38,230 --> 00:11:39,590
That is Master's exact foot size.

172
00:11:41,400 --> 00:11:42,160
A mere coincidence.

173
00:11:43,820 --> 00:11:45,280
How could Master be a murderer?

174
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:46,840
Commissioner Di,

175
00:11:47,066 --> 00:11:48,800
it's the work of the Red-Faced Guardian!

176
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:49,690
Ming Yu,

177
00:11:50,270 --> 00:11:51,030
someone has died!

178
00:11:51,070 --> 00:11:52,040
Tell them the truth.

179
00:11:52,088 --> 00:11:54,200
Remember how Master
has been acting weird lately?

180
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:54,840
Stop talking!

181
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,160
What is going on?

182
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:07,680
Get out!

183
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,800
Get out of my body!

184
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:17,880
Get out!

185
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,160
(Over a month ago,)

186
00:12:20,680 --> 00:12:22,360
(Master was like a changed person.)

187
00:12:23,222 --> 00:12:24,760
(He started berating and hitting me.)

188
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:27,760
(But he was even more cruel to himself.)

189
00:12:28,400 --> 00:12:29,500
(In the dead of winter,)

190
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,022
(he would dance barefoot endlessly)

191
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:32,440
(despite the frostbite)

192
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:34,000
(on his feet.)

193
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,360
(It was as if his body wasn't his own.)

194
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,560
(As if the Red-Faced Guardian)

195
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:44,920
(possessed him.)

196
00:12:49,822 --> 00:12:51,520
Master has indeed
been acting strangely,

197
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,680
but he could never be the murderer.

198
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,955
This must be divine punishment,
Commissioner Di.

199
00:13:01,570 --> 00:13:02,360
Commissioner Di!

200
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:05,120
Commissioner Di!

201
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:07,860
(Gongsun Heng, Prefect of Raozhou)

202
00:13:07,880 --> 00:13:09,520
Gongsun Heng, Prefect of Raozhou.

203
00:13:09,911 --> 00:13:11,511
Greetings, Imperial Commissioner.

204
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,840
Some members of the troupe

205
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,377
went to the Bureau to report the crime.

206
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,240
They said a commissioner was present,

207
00:13:16,720 --> 00:13:17,880
so I guessed

208
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:19,311
it must be you, Commissioner Di.

209
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,560
I just wanted

210
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:23,000
to catch a Nuo opera performance
and enjoy the festivities,

211
00:13:23,270 --> 00:13:25,880
but I didn't expect
to run into a homicide.

212
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,310
That's my oversight.

213
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,720
With the holidays approaching,

214
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,040
we should be much more vigilant.

215
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,360
Please, Prefect Gongsun,

216
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,080
seal off the news of the deceased

217
00:13:34,560 --> 00:13:35,600
and have your men

218
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,200
transport the body to the Bureau.

219
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,120
Yes.

220
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,000
However,

221
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,880
I heard

222
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:45,080
that Master Zhuang is a suspect.

223
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:47,080
Prefect,

224
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:48,560
why are you reacting like that?

225
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,280
It's nothing.

226
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,160
Zhuang Luobai

227
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,320
is the top

228
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:57,300
Nuo opera master in Raozhou.

229
00:13:57,910 --> 00:13:58,920
I've heard that

230
00:13:58,920 --> 00:14:01,000
he usually dislikes socializing

231
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,800
and is only obsessed with Nuo opera.

232
00:14:03,355 --> 00:14:04,560
I never would've imagined

233
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,800
he was hiding a secret.

234
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:08,720
Where is Zhuang Luobai?

235
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,720
Our men are looking for him.

236
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:12,680
Once he's found,

237
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:14,360
bring him in for questioning.

238
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,200
Yes.

239
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,600
Whether this footprint is a coincidence

240
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,640
or the truth

241
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:19,720
remains unclear.

242
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,600
We need more evidence.

243
00:14:21,920 --> 00:14:22,800
Just make sure

244
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:24,730
he doesn't leave Wangnian County.

245
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:26,760
Yes, Commissioner Di.

246
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,080
(Based on the footprint,)

247
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:35,080
(the foot length is 27.33 cm.)

248
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:36,720
(What?)

249
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,640
(That is Master's exact foot size.)

250
00:14:48,330 --> 00:14:48,960
Commissioner Di,

251
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,600
the victim's family is here.

252
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,160
Pan'er!

253
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,940
(Gu Qi, Father of Gu Pan'er)

254
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:57,120
(Hou Guangming, Vice Director)
My Pan'er!

255
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:00,760
With you gone,

256
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:03,830
- what am I supposed to do?
- Sir, please accept my condolences.

257
00:15:06,040 --> 00:15:06,840
Sir,

258
00:15:07,650 --> 00:15:08,960
yesterday morning,

259
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,960
I couldn't find Pan'er.

260
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:12,600
I thought

261
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:15,720
she'd gone to visit her in-laws,

262
00:15:16,044 --> 00:15:17,360
so I didn't think much of it.

263
00:15:21,560 --> 00:15:22,840
But who would've thought...

264
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:29,040
Her in-laws?

265
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:32,080
They didn't look down on me,

266
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,200
and let me

267
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,080
marry Pan'er.

268
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:40,480
Did Pan'er have any close friends?

269
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,640
Has she seen anyone lately?

270
00:15:43,880 --> 00:15:45,400
Sir,

271
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:47,560
Pan'er didn't really

272
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:48,720
have any close friends.

273
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,520
I...

274
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:53,960
I know who killed Pan'er!

275
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:56,550
It must be Zhuang Luobai!

276
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,720
What makes you say that?

277
00:15:58,800 --> 00:15:59,880
Before Pan'er was married,

278
00:16:00,640 --> 00:16:02,290
she and Zhuang Luobai

279
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:05,400
already knew each other.

280
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:06,900
Back then,

281
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,440
he relentlessly tried

282
00:16:09,440 --> 00:16:10,800
to seduce Pan'er.

283
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,920
He acts like a man of high morals,

284
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,480
but who knew he's actually

285
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:18,720
a heartless beast?

286
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:22,000
Even after Pan'er got married,

287
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:24,200
he kept pestering her.

288
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:27,040
She must have rejected him,

289
00:16:27,680 --> 00:16:28,940
and he held a grudge,

290
00:16:29,010 --> 00:16:30,950
which led him to kill her.

291
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:35,920
Please, justice must be served!

292
00:16:37,390 --> 00:16:38,960
If there is concrete evidence,

293
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:42,080
the Bureau will
ensure justice is served.

294
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:44,920
Thank you, sir.

295
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:45,920
Guards,

296
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,520
send him out.

297
00:16:52,550 --> 00:16:53,990
This case is interesting.

298
00:16:54,820 --> 00:16:56,680
Everyone is adamant

299
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,800
that Zhuang Luobai is the killer.

300
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,960
You mean to say

301
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:02,440
someone else is the killer?

302
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:05,160
If this were a crime of passion,

303
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,720
why would Zhuang Luobai drag the body

304
00:17:07,720 --> 00:17:08,840
back to the theater?

305
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,800
Everyone there knows

306
00:17:10,840 --> 00:17:12,440
he and Gu Pan'er had a past.

307
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,910
Isn't that just

308
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:15,560
asking to be caught?

309
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:18,680
This has to be a set-up.

310
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,110
But according to Prefect Gongsun,

311
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:23,480
Zhuang Luobai stays inside all day,

312
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,720
obsessed with his dancing.

313
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:27,050
How could he have enemies?

314
00:17:27,130 --> 00:17:29,740
Why would anyone bother framing him?

315
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:31,900
Duan,

316
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:34,000
dig deeper into Gu Pan'er.

317
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:34,680
Understood.

318
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:47,120
Again.

319
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,200
Again.

320
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:53,120
Master,

321
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,280
I've been watching.

322
00:17:54,840 --> 00:17:56,000
Nothing unusual so far.

323
00:17:56,570 --> 00:17:58,050
It's not as sinister as they say.

324
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:00,280
He just has a bit of a temper.

325
00:18:01,530 --> 00:18:02,720
- Again.
- Zhuang Luobai

326
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:03,920
is a man obsessed.

327
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:06,200
Sir,

328
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:08,210
do you think he's the killer?

329
00:18:09,610 --> 00:18:11,960
An obsessed man can become a saint,

330
00:18:13,060 --> 00:18:14,400
or he can become a devil.

331
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,360
If you don't practice hard,

332
00:18:21,200 --> 00:18:22,640
you'll embarrass yourself on stage.

333
00:18:23,022 --> 00:18:25,160
If you perform
the God-Welcoming Dance this way,

334
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:27,440
how can you be the lead dancer
for the Winter Festival?

335
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:32,480
You useless fool!

336
00:18:55,111 --> 00:18:56,360
Are you out of your mind?

337
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,640
You could've beaten him to death.

338
00:18:59,080 --> 00:19:00,240
My business

339
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:01,240
is none of your concern.

340
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:03,400
Sir,

341
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,200
if you have evidence,

342
00:19:05,890 --> 00:19:07,620
then send men to arrest me.

343
00:19:08,240 --> 00:19:09,360
If you don't,

344
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,370
then stop interfering.

345
00:19:11,940 --> 00:19:12,960
Gu Pan'er was innocent.

346
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:15,440
You and Gu Pan'er were friends.

347
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:17,790
Please, enlighten me.

348
00:19:33,010 --> 00:19:35,080
Why is Master so polite to him?

349
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:37,120
They're all too high-minded.

350
00:19:37,444 --> 00:19:38,920
Too refined for the common folk.

351
00:19:39,800 --> 00:19:40,560
Too what?

352
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:44,040
Talk less, and read more.

353
00:19:46,660 --> 00:19:48,120
But I can't read.

354
00:19:56,360 --> 00:19:57,880
When was the last time

355
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:59,000
you saw her?

356
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,560
Over a month ago.

357
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:08,120
How did you and Gu Pan'er

358
00:20:08,120 --> 00:20:09,680
meet each other?

359
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:14,040
This time, a year ago,

360
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:17,600
it was snowing just like this.

361
00:20:20,320 --> 00:20:21,840
(Back then, Pan'er)

362
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,360
(was still an innocent girl.)

363
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:27,440
(Just like this white snow,)

364
00:20:29,040 --> 00:20:31,440
(untouched by the world.)

365
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:37,400
Come in.

366
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:45,120
Are you

367
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:46,680
really Zhuang Luobai?

368
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:49,400
You're actually so handsome.

369
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:52,320
I've only ever seen you wearing a mask.

370
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:53,970
I've never seen the real you.

371
00:20:58,080 --> 00:20:59,520
Whether I'm wearing a mask or not,

372
00:21:00,120 --> 00:21:01,320
I'm still the real me.

373
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:07,960
Do you like this?

374
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:09,640
Yes.

375
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:13,840
Women can't touch the mask.

376
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:15,688
It offends the Red-Faced Guardian.

377
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:19,720
If you truly hold it dear,

378
00:21:20,520 --> 00:21:21,360
how could it

379
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:22,560
be offensive?

380
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:29,720
(Since then,)

381
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:32,360
(we've become good friends.)

382
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,600
(She often came backstage)

383
00:21:36,711 --> 00:21:38,160
(and had me teach her Nuo dancing.)

384
00:21:40,050 --> 00:21:41,680
(Many are obsessed with Nuo opera,)

385
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:45,280
(but she was the first woman)

386
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,000
(brave enough)

387
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,840
(to step into the backstage.)

388
00:21:52,160 --> 00:21:54,160
(I'd never seen the purity and beauty)

389
00:21:55,130 --> 00:21:56,440
(in her eyes before.)

390
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:00,160
This year's Winter Festival performance

391
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,480
was inspired by her.

392
00:22:02,910 --> 00:22:04,160
The Winter Festival?

393
00:22:05,040 --> 00:22:06,080
For a Nuo performer,

394
00:22:06,080 --> 00:22:07,600
the culmination of my life

395
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,960
is this grand performance of the year.

396
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,000
May I hear about this dance,

397
00:22:13,720 --> 00:22:15,360
Master Zhuang?

398
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:18,680
She was pure radiance,
untainted by the world,

399
00:22:20,270 --> 00:22:21,280
yet the world

400
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:23,740
trapped her in a cage.

401
00:22:24,460 --> 00:22:25,520
She fought back.

402
00:22:25,810 --> 00:22:27,310
She couldn't break free in the end,

403
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:28,670
but she still

404
00:22:29,390 --> 00:22:30,920
managed to bloom for a while.

405
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,120
The bond between you two

406
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:35,880
wasn't about the dance,

407
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,400
was it?

408
00:22:38,760 --> 00:22:39,760
Pan'er

409
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:41,680
and I

410
00:22:43,120 --> 00:22:45,040
were trapped by these shackles.

411
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,240
Just two miserable souls

412
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:50,120
who could never break free from them.

413
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:26,440
My dear,

414
00:23:27,640 --> 00:23:29,800
please, just have a bite.

415
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:33,080
Pan'er is already gone.

416
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:34,880
Do you really

417
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:37,760
intend to follow her to death?

418
00:23:44,440 --> 00:23:45,720
Zhuang Luobai

419
00:23:46,740 --> 00:23:49,640
brought the Red-Faced Guardian's curse.

420
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:52,390
None of us can escape it.

421
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:02,840
My dear!

422
00:24:07,300 --> 00:24:08,420
(Preview of Next Episode)

423
00:24:12,990 --> 00:24:14,970
Help!

424
00:24:39,470 --> 00:24:41,050
♪Night covers the long streets♪

425
00:24:42,130 --> 00:24:43,840
♪The city remains silent♪

426
00:24:45,230 --> 00:24:46,820
♪Wind turns the old pages♪

427
00:24:47,080 --> 00:24:49,320
♪Words still left unspoken♪

428
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,360
♪Bloodstains still hold their warmth♪

429
00:24:53,490 --> 00:24:55,960
♪Lamplight slowly tilts aside♪

430
00:24:56,580 --> 00:24:58,060
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

431
00:24:58,060 --> 00:25:01,200
♪Still circling around the truth?♪

432
00:25:01,820 --> 00:25:03,740
♪Love is born from desire♪

433
00:25:04,430 --> 00:25:06,560
♪Hatred rises out of greed♪

434
00:25:07,700 --> 00:25:09,360
♪One thought becomes a snare♪

435
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:12,660
♪A lifetime trapped within♪

436
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:15,430
♪Someone once warned me♪

437
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:16,950
♪To stop upon this shore♪

438
00:25:16,950 --> 00:25:18,270
♪But sunlight burns too fiercely♪

439
00:25:18,270 --> 00:25:19,760
♪Fragile eyes break too easily♪

440
00:25:19,760 --> 00:25:20,880
♪If one thought retreats♪

441
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:22,180
♪Then all things rest in peace♪

442
00:25:22,180 --> 00:25:23,520
♪But in this world♪

443
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:25,920
♪Who will make the final judgment?♪

444
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:30,560
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

445
00:25:30,560 --> 00:25:32,030
♪Still I walk ahead♪

446
00:25:32,260 --> 00:25:33,480
♪Let it pierce through♪

447
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:38,220
♪The illusions before my eyes♪

448
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:40,460
♪Layer upon layer of deception♪

449
00:25:40,460 --> 00:25:41,860
♪Covering every heart♪

450
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:43,050
♪How many people♪

451
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,680
♪Weave their own cocoon♪

452
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,890
♪Yet call it♪

453
00:25:47,090 --> 00:25:48,430
♪Fate?♪

454
00:25:48,790 --> 00:25:49,970
♪Life and death♪

455
00:25:49,970 --> 00:25:51,230
♪Balanced on a single line♪

456
00:25:51,580 --> 00:25:52,750
♪Light and shadow♪

457
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:54,010
♪Hanging side by side♪

458
00:25:54,010 --> 00:25:55,490
♪Goodness is not absolute♪

459
00:25:55,490 --> 00:25:56,900
♪Nor is evil ever complete♪

460
00:25:56,900 --> 00:25:58,440
♪In the end, it is only♪

461
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,820
♪A single misguided thought♪

462
00:25:59,820 --> 00:26:01,380
♪If unveiling the truth♪

463
00:26:01,380 --> 00:26:02,720
♪Requires abandoning tenderness♪

464
00:26:02,720 --> 00:26:03,890
♪Then this answer♪

465
00:26:03,890 --> 00:26:05,250
♪Can it still remain true?♪

466
00:26:05,250 --> 00:26:06,650
♪When love and law♪

467
00:26:06,650 --> 00:26:08,130
♪Stand against each other in silence♪

468
00:26:08,130 --> 00:26:09,530
♪Which figure before me♪

469
00:26:09,530 --> 00:26:16,730
♪Am I meant to believe?♪

470
00:26:16,730 --> 00:26:19,460
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

471
00:26:19,460 --> 00:26:21,050
♪Still I walk ahead♪

472
00:26:21,050 --> 00:26:22,290
♪Not for fame or glory♪

473
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:27,160
♪Nor caring who wins or loses♪

474
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,970
♪Human nature is clouded♪

475
00:26:28,970 --> 00:26:30,690
♪Yet still reflects the stars♪

476
00:26:30,690 --> 00:26:32,160
♪Though this world♪

477
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,530
♪Is filled with mud and mire♪

478
00:26:33,530 --> 00:26:35,780
♪There is still a light♪

479
00:26:35,780 --> 00:26:38,740
♪Worth pursuing♪

480
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:40,560
♪Every case has its ending♪

481
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:41,820
♪But night does not always fade♪

482
00:26:42,090 --> 00:26:43,470
♪The wind stops, the pages close♪

483
00:26:43,470 --> 00:26:44,690
♪Yet hearts remain unsettled♪

484
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:46,040
♪If justice stands♪

485
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:47,290
♪Without mercy beside it♪

486
00:26:47,290 --> 00:26:49,090
♪Then how is it♪

487
00:26:49,090 --> 00:26:58,650
♪Any different from a blade?♪

488
00:26:58,650 --> 00:27:01,840
♪If truth is cold as a frosted blade♪

489
00:27:01,840 --> 00:27:03,320
♪Still I walk ahead♪

490
00:27:03,320 --> 00:27:04,710
♪Even if the world♪

491
00:27:04,710 --> 00:27:09,440
♪Refuses to answer♪

492
00:27:09,440 --> 00:27:11,400
♪When every hidden truth♪

493
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:13,110
♪Finally reveals itself♪

494
00:27:13,110 --> 00:27:14,470
♪I only wish♪

495
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:15,950
♪To hold on♪

496
00:27:15,950 --> 00:27:20,690
♪Within the darkness♪

497
00:27:20,690 --> 00:27:22,690
♪To the heart♪

